      "span_text": "This follows from the fact that the embedding of the Schrödinger algebra into the AdS isometry algebra is essentially unique [CITATION_1] and that this embedding is such that the Schrödinger algebra consists of all those AdS 5 isometries that commute with a null Killing vector."
